{
  "texts": [
    "Each prompt button is represented by an emoji icon and corresponds to a prompt template.",
    "Users can click the prompt button to run its prompt using the current paragraph as the input text.",
    "If a user has selected some text, the selected text is used as the input for the prompt.",
    "Users can also click the home button to open a pop-up window that contains the Personal Prompt Library ( § 3.2, Fig. 2A), the Community Prompt Hub ( § 3.3, Fig.",
    "1B), and the Setting Panel (Fig. 4).Prompt input templating."
  ]
}